title: DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller & Chico Bean Pay Homage To Rap's Legends | Hip Hop Awards '21
author: BETNetworks
description:
DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller and Chico Bean aka 85 South opened up the BET Hip Hop Awards paying homage to rap stars like Pimp C and Soulja Boy.
